# Strobe Engine — the riser: 2600-style hard sync, VCO1 mastering
# VCO2's ramp reset. Hold one note and ramp osc2_pitch upward and the
# reset comb sweeps through the harmonic series — the classic sync
# scream. The Moog ladder (circuit 0) driven hot so the resonance
# sings along with it.
waveform 2
osc2_wave 2
osc2_pitch 0
osc2_level 1.0
osc3_wave 2
osc3_pitch 0
osc3_level 0
detune 0
sub 0
circuit 0
key_track 1.0
osc_fm 0
sync 1
ring 0
glide 0
pulse_width 0.5
attack 0.02
decay 0.5
sustain 0.85
release 0.3
filter_env 0.8
filter_attack 0.3
filter_decay 0.5
filter_sustain 0.6
filter_release 0.3
cutoff 700
resonance 2.4
drive 2.2
saturation 1.2
hpf 60
volume 0.65
noise 0.06
fuzz 0
